heating, 穿牆, 加速, 一槍死乜都有齊<br />\n而且係無得fix, 因為用左client authoritative network model</blockquote><br />\nclient authoritative network model＜咩黎?"},{"pid":"42bfdc2fbc46b0e199e51e9e3b7d81e2aaa632f6","tid":179136,"uid":52876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T16:47:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢隻game垃圾, 尤其pc版<br />\n勁多cheating, 穿牆, 加速, 一槍死乜都有齊<br />\n而且係無得fix, 因為用左client authoritative network model</blockquote><br />\nclient authoritative network model＜咩黎?</blockquote><br />\n大部份competitive既multiplayer game都係sever authoritative<br />\n即係每個client每秒都會poll至少30次inputs同send去個sever到做simulation<br />\n雖然都會幫local player既做client side prediction去消除server同client之間既delay<br />\n但係client既作用只係重現返sever既simulation results<br />\n<br />\n但係client authoritative既話, 就係client做完simulation, 再將個result send去個server<br />\n即係如果你修改個client既program, 你想點cheat就點cheat, 因為個sever無做任何simulation"},{"pid":"d1a88e4a090f573666bf9e7239e1bd6f0792a2c5","tid":179136,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:20:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢隻game垃圾, 尤其pc版<br />\n勁多cheating, 穿牆, 加速, 一槍死乜都有齊<br />\n而且係無得fix, 因為用左client authoritative network model</blockquote><br />\nclient authoritative network model＜咩黎?</blockquote><br />\n大部份competitive既multiplayer game都係sever authoritative<br />\n即係每個client每秒都會poll至少30次inputs同send去個sever到做simulation<br />\n雖然都會幫local player既做client side prediction去消除server同client之間既delay<br />\n但係client既作用只係重現返sever既simulation results<br />\n<br />\n但係client authoritative既話, 就係client做完simulation, 再將個result send去個server<br />\n即係如果你修改個client既program, 你想點cheat就點cheat, 因為個sever無做任何simulation</blockquote><br />\n學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2773965d0180a42d3990db821c032eb68ee67e0b","tid":179136,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T14:13:07.000Z","msg":"有無人玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b7bc5c2958577c431273774289c9680bd176b3","tid":179136,"uid":84507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T20:43:42.000Z","msg":"呢隻GAME 係痴撚線既<br />\n嗱SERVER 癈同有BUG 果D 唔多講，有CHEAT 都唔多講<br />\nSERVER 廢如果少人玩就自然會改善<br />\nBUG 可以FIX 或者其實只係因為SERVER 廢搞到有BUG<br />\n有CHEAT 就隻隻GAME 都係咁，冇辦法<br />\n<br />\n但係隻GAME 係成個設計有問題<br />\n先講好先，個關卡設計世界級，係好野來，你入去每一個關卡都見佢D 野SET 得好好，PVP 果D 唔係關卡唔計<br />\n<br />\n但係作為一隻ONLINE GAME........PVP 裝備平衡呢？<br />\n最基本技能平衡都做唔好<br />\n跟住唔PVP 喇，淨打怪咁點解連公會都冇.......今時今日ONLINE GAME 連公會都冇，死得啦<br />\n<br />\n根本整呢隻GAME 果陣就係咁諗，嗱我用整MMO 既方法來整一隻單機GAME<br />\n淨係賣正價果段時間(賣左成幾百萬隻架)，已經夠回哂製作同SERVER、廣告成本<br />\n跟住特價再有人買，咪淨賺囉！<br />\n嗱我再出SEASON PASS，又係做返果堆野只係畫下新地圖，如果有人仲買，咪淨賺囉......<br />\n果D 人仲玩唔玩落去，關我叉事？我都收左錢，而且只係需要收一次錢<br />\n<br />\n即係你會見到DESTINY 都係玩刷野RPG/射擊GAME，但係人地KEEP 住有新活動，地圖，公會，新內容除左賣SEASON PASS，為左維持SERVER 繼續有人玩要不停出新裝備，新LEVEL.....跟住出課金時裝賺你錢，好明顯DESTINY 就係真ONLINE GAME 思維，想你KEEP 住玩繼續賺你錢唔係呃你一筆跟住就關我叉事......<br />\n<br />\n呢度已經睇到DIVISION 點解咁快死"},{"pid":"f6578d521d1d7085c7fa48f1d62d17d1e5fb21df","tid":179136,"uid":77760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T23:52:34.000Z","msg":"之前打到30lv就冇玩<br />\n<br />\n連大使館果啲副本都未打<br />\n<br />\n有冇人一齊玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2335c415b4519ecf55a2dd31374a850e9abc4f92","tid":179136,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T08:29:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前打到30lv就冇玩<br />\n<br />\n連大使館果啲副本都未打<br />\n<br />\n有冇人一齊玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\npc 定ps4?"},{"pid":"ee7e9837d1cf82fc5826f7539da90c8811e98f21","tid":179136,"uid":77760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前打到30lv就冇玩<br />\n<br />\n連大使館果啲副本都未打<br />\n<br />\n有冇人一齊玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\npc 定ps4?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPs4"},{"p